Chapter 10 — Synthesis: The Energy Requirements for Autonomous Intelligence

10.1 The Φ-E Loop

We have established a feedback loop between energy and information:

E \xrightarrow{\text{powers}} \Phi \xrightarrow{\text{enables}} \text{Better energy technology} \xrightarrow{\text{provides}} E

